description:
The Girls Guide to Depravity Season 1 (13 episodes)

I downloaded the entire season 1 but the files seemed to have an issue as they were all 1 hour long so I remuxed them and now they play fine and the size is adequate. 

Episodes 1-2 are from xiaofriend and all other episodes are from CHDTV.

I will be seeding this file 10x and then quit so beware of hit & run.

Enjoy and keep seeding when you're done.
